# Copy this file to .Renviron and fill in your ESPN credentials.
# Then restart R for the values to take effect.
#
# To find these values:
#   1. Log into fantasy.espn.com in your browser
#   2. Open Developer Tools (F12)
#   3. Go to Application (Chrome) or Storage (Firefox) > Cookies > fantasy.espn.com
#   4. Copy the values for espn_s2 and SWID
#
# The .Renviron file is gitignored so your credentials stay local.

ESPN_S2=paste_your_espn_s2_cookie_here
ESPN_SWID={paste-your-swid-here}
